55</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/async_function\"><code>async function function</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/async_function\"><code>async function expression</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function\"><code>Function</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/function\"><code>function statement</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/function\"><code>function expression</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Functions\">Funções e escopo de função <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Descrição","id":"descrição"},{"text":"Propriedas","id":"propriedas"},{"text":"<code>AsyncFunction&nbsp;</code>prototype object","id":"asyncfunction_prototype_object"},{"text":"<code>AsyncFunction</code> instances","id":"asyncfunction_instances"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O construtor AsyncFunction cria um novo objeto async function. Em JavaScript cada função assíncrona é atualmente um objeto do tipo AsyncFunction.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"AsyncFunction","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"AsyncFunction","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Funciones asíncronas","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"AsyncFunction","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"AsyncFunction","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"AsyncFunction","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"AsyncFunction","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"AsyncFunction","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"AsyncFunction","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/asyncfunction","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/asyncfunction/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"Referência JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Objetos Globais"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/AsyncFunction","title":"AsyncFunction"}],"pageTitle":"AsyncFunction - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}